Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.49,0:03:35.20,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\be10\blur5\an2\pos(640,656)\fs30} ※此話中出現的劇本台詞均出自《奧賽羅》第三幕第三場。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一方面又是那樣痴心疼愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}這才是活活的受罪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 表演的日子馬上就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好緊張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.46,0:03:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}桃子你練習了那麼多肯定很輕鬆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.18,0:03:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 正式表演會如何誰也說不準啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}總之 只要能快快樂樂地表演就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真不愧是你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吶 七海你台詞都背好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.52,0:03:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}七海？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.32,0:04:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 難說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.16,0:04:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們都指望著你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家一起加油 讓我們組全員都合格吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.30,0:04:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我必 須更努力才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.58,0:04:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}買東西回來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.24,0:04:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天吃蛋包飯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的 做起來比較省事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}覺得做蛋包飯比較省事的七海
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}女性魅力簡直像喜馬拉雅山一樣高
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.02,0:04:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太誇張啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.82,0:04:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我去叫學弟和仁過來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.26,0:04:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 今天我值日 我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.16,0:04:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太過完美？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.36,0:04:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}椎名同學 吃晚飯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.08,0:04:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}發售日是…指雜誌的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟我的表演是同一天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就快到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}椎名同學 我幫你把扣子縫上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.36,0:05:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}另外記得把要洗的衣服拿出來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}您要留心嫉妒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嫉妒是一個綠眼的妖魔…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.88,0:05:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰做了它的犧牲 就要受它的玩弄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}七海太緊崩了...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在煩惱桃花期遲遲不來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:46.83,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\be10\blur5}※ 日本有個傳說 每人一生會有三次受歡迎的時期。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是都市傳說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.08,0:05:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都說不是…咦 是真的嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虧我還一直相信著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過你的情況 就是發現沒發現的問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:05:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個 仁學長 有時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}於是 想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是關於青山的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被告白了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.50,0:06:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}戲弄我就那麼好玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.48,0:06:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}擔心青山同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}與其說是擔心…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山確實精明能幹 大部份的事情都能做得比一般人好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.74,0:06:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是所有事一個人全包了也太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.12,0:06:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}畢竟大家住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.16,0:06:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}互相幫助也沒什麼不可以的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟我對青山同學的印像大不一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.94,0:06:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}算了 但是我想青山同學她也有很多自己的想法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.40,0:06:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}找到了目標 不顧父母的反對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.32,0:06:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}走出家門之後一直都是靠自己一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想她一定覺得無論什麼事都必須自己解決吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有真白的事也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦？椎名？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}像這種事唯有她本人認可才行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}意思是讓我別管她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是我的話會這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:06:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}空太你會如何抉擇我就不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}思考是一件好事哦 學弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.76,0:07:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別用那種叫法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大阪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}仁學長 這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如你所見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不會去水明大學 而是去大阪的藝術大學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.80,0:07:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那美{\r}{\blur5\fnＦＡ 丸ゴシックＭ\fs42}咲{\r}{\blur5}學姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.78,0:07:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們又不是在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別跟美{\r}{\blur5\fnＦＡ 丸ゴシックＭ\fs42}咲{\r}{\blur5}說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.12,0:07:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會自己對她說的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.92,0:07:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你別一副那麼深沉的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一如既往 你什麼都不知道 很簡單的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.26,0:07:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今後叫我怎麼面對美{\r}{\blur5\fnＦＡ 丸ゴシックＭ\fs42}咲{\r}{\blur5}學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}仁學長到底想怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼面對我是指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你什麼時候開始在那裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才剛到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}仁怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.92,0:08:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 啊 那個…是跟他談了關於策劃書的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}完全沒有提到關於美{\r}{\blur5\fnＦＡ 丸ゴシックＭ\fs42}咲{\r}{\blur5}學姐的話題啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦 我？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯... 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}美...美{\r}{\blur5\fnＦＡ 丸ゴシックＭ\fs42}咲{\r}{\blur5}學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.98,0:08:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吶 學弟…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼做…才能讓仁留意到我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學姐想和仁學長成為什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼關係…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}像戀人般 親吻之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.60,0:08:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想牽著手一起散步 想被他緊緊抱住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是我不知道該怎麼做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.74,0:08:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家都是怎麼成為戀人的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學弟…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.26,0:09:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學姐很可愛的所以沒關係的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了打起精神要來打場遊戲嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.06,0:09:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}竟敢挑戰我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}成長了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學弟 暑假剩下的時間裡 我們盡情地去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對我和仁來說這是最後的暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.66,0:09:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.56,0:09:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你沒事吧 別太勉強了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起 我不小心絆了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我真是笨拙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.56,0:10:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.64,0:10:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}10
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}9
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.64,0:10:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}8
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.26,0:10:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}7…啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.48,0:10:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}空太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}七海很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.04,0:10:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.28,0:10:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了怎麼了 真白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.54,0:10:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}七海怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.12,0:10:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}七海
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.56,0:10:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 青山 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.18,0:10:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要去 今天一定要去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.72,0:10:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拜託了 讓我去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}偏偏是在這種時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然我早就覺得她這樣勉強自己遲早會出問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聲優培訓所的表演是今天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.38,0:11:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想她是為了不讓我們注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.34,0:11:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才想早點出門的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然本人是想去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不可能讓她去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.18,0:11:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然很可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.06,0:11:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.46,0:11:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}換做我的話我會去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.98,0:11:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是我的話 我會去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 椎名…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既然七海想去的話 就讓她去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓她去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.64,0:11:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}七海 很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.82,0:11:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}每天練習到很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.62,0:11:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這些我當然知道 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}慢慢走就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.44,0:12:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吵死了 從剛才起你們在鬧什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.72,0:12:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你這麼高的燒還想出門？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去休息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.08,0:12:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我才不管你願不願意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回到房裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}計程車來了 快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.34,0:12:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}公主大人我們就接走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}等等 給我站住…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.50,0:12:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}空太 接下來就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}喂 你們幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.28,0:12:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}七海 坐好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學弟也快點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.64,0:12:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}上吧 上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}走吧 椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.84,0:12:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的 那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}前進吧 計程車 Go Go！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.52,0:12:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}三鷹 別趁亂摸我胸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為那裡有胸嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別說的像登山一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.82,0:12:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:12:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.82,0:13:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝 接下來我一個人就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}結束的時候我們也會在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.78,0:13:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.22,0:13:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山小姐 找你很久了 趕快進來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.10,0:13:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去咖啡店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就待在這
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.94,0:13:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有很長時間哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.22,0:13:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是因為我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}七海 太累了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不道歉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她肯定會生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.32,0:14:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雨下的真突然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}買把傘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.14,0:14:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.04,0:14:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「那到時候一起去買吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.76,0:14:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 慌慌張張的完全忘記是今天了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.78,0:14:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼會沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.48,0:14:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒必要執著於發售日
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看 這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.92,0:14:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不看一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.74,0:14:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}內容我都知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.76,0:14:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}即使如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.86,0:14:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}難道你不太高興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.54,0:14:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.92,0:14:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哇 果然下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.32,0:14:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跑步去車站
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.18,0:14:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦 不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:14:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:15:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等一下 七海
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.08,0:15:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你知道因為你的關係給大家添了多少麻煩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}與其發展成這樣 你還不如就待在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.42,0:15:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.46,0:15:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.92,0:15:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}給你們添了這麼多麻煩 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.36,0:15:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼都沒做成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}難得你們願意帶我來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.32,0:15:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明為了今天一直在準備
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.28,0:15:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}結果全都白費了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我太差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.92,0:15:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才不會沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你也說過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.66,0:16:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說我太逞強 太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.86,0:16:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}自己擔著這麼多工作 還以為能做的更好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}結果就一個勁地逞強 我真是個笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.76,0:16:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事的 青山
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不用在乎我說的那些話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.26,0:16:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.00,0:16:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說我是個傻女人 嘲笑我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不然的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.28,0:16:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不然的話 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.82,0:16:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別那樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.28,0:16:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果青山是笨蛋的話 世上的人豈不都成笨蛋了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.24,0:16:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼啊 別開玩笑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.58,0:16:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神田同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山已經很努力了 這點我們都很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼 為什麼要那麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽到你這樣說的話 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.70,0:16:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一直很希望能有人這樣對我說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.26,0:17:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}七海一直勉強著自己呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.22,0:17:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為她是那種對別人或自己都很嚴格的類型
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嘛 或許她只是想保持那樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我總算明白仁所說的「印像不同」的意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.94,0:17:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山一直在跟什麼奮戰著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}比如父母的反對 以及與自身等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也許是一直沒有可以依靠的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.40,0:17:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怕自己只要懈怠了一次 就會一錯再錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.10,0:17:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只能逞著強 把自己逼入了絕境
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能有人明白這一點 她也算是有所回報了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小真白還陪在青山身邊的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.94,0:17:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 好像有挺多放不下的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.42,0:18:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.84,0:18:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人參雞湯 我想這種時候還是來點特別的火鍋比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.86,0:18:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}特別？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為七海把脆弱的一面展露出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}脆弱的一面…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.34,0:18:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}話說人參雞湯根本不是火鍋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太在意細節的話 會錯過桃花期的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.82,0:18:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虎次郎 我該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\3c&H007FFF&}我怎麼會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 昨天也太難為情了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被他看到我哭得那麼慘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.42,0:18:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖說發燒了 但我一直都靠在他身上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.76,0:18:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\3c&H007FFF&}趁亂就黏著不放吶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.70,0:18:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我又不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\3c&H007FFF&}不要磨嘰磨嘰的 趕緊去推倒他吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等…虎次郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就是虎次郎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.62,0:19:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等...敲個門啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}敲了 而且門是開著的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.02,0:19:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}討厭…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.26,0:19:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真沒想到這個抱枕 原來還有說話功能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.88,0:19:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別告訴別人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.86,0:19:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是糟透了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.44,0:19:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}給
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這個樣子好像不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.00,0:19:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.66,0:19:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不快點吃就冷掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.64,0:19:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.14,0:19:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要謝的話就謝仁學長吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.32,0:19:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 好像整夜都握著我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.26,0:19:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}似乎是感覺到了責任
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.64,0:19:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:20:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且 最了解青山的人是椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要不是椎名的話 我就阻止你去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.38,0:20:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 她說「換做是我的話 我會去」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「請帶她去吧」 向大家低下了頭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你努力的樣子她一直都看在眼裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.72,0:20:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.52,0:20:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果沒去的話 我肯定會後悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.48,0:20:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看著椎名 我就會覺得自己做得還遠遠不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.96,0:20:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.20,0:20:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}每天都畫漫畫到很晚 一遍又一遍地改過重畫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我原以為有才能的人是不會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.08,0:20:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要怎麼做 才能追上有才能的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}追上…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.34,0:20:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別盯著看！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.20,0:20:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}椎名同學的睡臉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.36,0:20:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看房間也不行！也不許看我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那我該看哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.74,0:20:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有不許太接近我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:20:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}總覺得有點受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.78,0:21:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為 我都還沒洗澡…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.54,0:21:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是說人參雞湯很好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.68,0:21:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早安 椎名同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.48,0:21:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}七海 已經沒事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.22,0:21:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 多虧了你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.88,0:21:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神田同學 關於照顧真白的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 說實話我沒有辦法繼續照顧她了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.90,0:21:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然不是照顧不了她 但以我現在的處境…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.18,0:21:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我明白了 謝謝你 願意依靠我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.78,0:21:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}該道謝的是我 抱歉 椎名同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.68,0:21:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}希望七海能叫我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.56,0:21:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道了 真白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.52,0:21:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.10,0:21:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等等 椎…真白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.64,0:21:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神田同學 想想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.18,0:21:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}負責照顧她的人是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.95,0:21:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1vc(&H53515C&,&H729CC0&,&H384550&,&H729CC0&)\shad0\fs45\bord0\move(504,203.2,432,179.2,22,7779)}『真白的保姆』由青山七海變回神田空太。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.95,0:21:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1vc(&H384550&,&H729CC0&,&H384550&,&H384550&)\shad0\fs45\bord0\move(480,532.2,411.2,557.8,22,7779)}神田同學，給你添了不少麻煩對不起。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.95,0:21:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H384550&\shad0\fs45\bord0\move(406.4,596.2,334.4,631.4,22,7779)}有句話忘說了就寫在這裡吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.95,0:21:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H384550&\shad0\fs45\bord0\move(598.4,661.8,528,709.8,22,7779)}要是敢對真白做什麼奇怪的事情的話 我絕饒不了你！
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.44,0:21:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}事已至此 為時已晚了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.76,0:21:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}打也打不醒的
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.96,0:21:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快起來 真白 真白！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:05.31,NCED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}過ぎるだけの  時間じゃ悔しい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:05.31,NCED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}一味流逝的時光 徒增懊悔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.77,0:22:07.89,NCED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}刻まなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.77,0:22:07.89,NCED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}唯有銘記於心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.27,0:22:14.15,NCED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}「此処にいる」と心が叫ぶ瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.27,0:22:14.15,NCED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}「我就在這裡」 內心如此吶喊的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.40,0:22:16.69,NCED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}I'm dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.40,0:22:16.69,NCED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}I'm dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.82,0:22:23.33,NCED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}迷いながら  涙を飲み込んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.82,0:22:23.33,NCED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}不斷迷茫著 逞強噙住眼角淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.83,0:22:29.46,NCED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}不器用だね　夢も遠回り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.83,0:22:29.46,NCED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}真是笨拙呢 連夢想都不斷繞道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.83,0:22:35.46,NCED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}大空を見上げ　何も見えず
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.83,0:22:35.46,NCED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}仰望這片廣闊的天空 卻無法確認一物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.76,0:22:43.76,NCED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}胸が痛むわけ考えていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.76,0:22:43.76,NCED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}也曾思考過內心會如此疼痛的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.01,0:22:45.35,NCED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}DAYS  of  DASH
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.01,0:22:45.35,NCED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}DAYS of DASH
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.35,0:22:48.14,NCED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}風を走り抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.35,0:22:48.14,NCED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}飛奔而出 風聲過耳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.35,0:22:54.57,NCED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}君と僕の中で　何が始まったのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.35,0:22:54.57,NCED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}在你與我的內心中 究竟有什麼開始了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.65,0:22:56.65,NCED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}わからないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.65,0:22:56.65,NCED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}雖然沒有答案
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.82,0:23:04.24,NCED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}キラキラ光る太陽が照らす場所をずっと進もう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.82,0:23:04.24,NCED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}但是就向著炫目陽光照耀的地方一直前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.45,0:23:10.12,NCED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}永遠など　知らないけれど
